==Swedish==
===Noun===
{{sv-noun-reg-er}}
'''mängd''' {{c}}

#[[amount]]; a quantity or a volume
#:''En stor '''mängd''' sand'' = ''Lots of sand''
#[[crowd]]; a number of things collected
#:''En '''mängd''' leksaker lades under dynorna där barnen lekte'' = ''A crowd of toys were pushed beneath the couch where the children were playing.
#crowd; a large congregated group of people 
#:''Så fort dörrarna öppnades strömmade '''mängden''' in'' = ''As soon as the doors were opened the crowed streamed inside''
#{{sv-mathematics}} [[set]]
#:'''''Mängden''' av de reella talen'' = ''The set of the real numbers''

